- Yes.

1960
02:03:35.809 --> 02:03:37.971
Hey kid.
it's been nice knowing you.

1961
02:03:38.154 --> 02:03:40.044
Remember what I did for my country.

1962
02:03:41.481 --> 02:03:42.962
This is my moment.

1963
02:03:44.162 --> 02:03:45.398
You're crazy!

1964
02:03:47.374 --> 02:03:49.220
ETA to station.
two minutes.

1965
02:03:49.255 --> 02:03:51.116
- Put it on the main screen.
- Sir. yes. sir.

1966
02:03:51.371 --> 02:03:52.404
Predator's airborne.

1967
02:04:02.828 --> 02:04:04.328
Oh shit. it's a trick.

1968
02:04:04.378 --> 02:04:06.827
Commence Operation Firestorm.
Send everyone.

1969
02:04:06.863 --> 02:04:09.690
- Get those boys out on the ground.*
- This is 101 in strike packages.*

1970
02:04:09.758 --> 02:04:11.372
Fast course river.* Execute lightly.

1971
02:04:31.694 --> 02:04:33.804
- Spotted Sam.
- Hurry. don't slow up!

1972
02:04:34.843 --> 02:04:36.089
Ironhide!

1973
02:04:36.856 --> 02:04:39.053
Follow us to the pillars.
We'll take you to Optimus.

1974
02:04:39.188 --> 02:04:39.890
Look out!

1975
02:04:42.893 --> 02:04:44.977
Sam. get to the pillars!

1976
02:04:46.251 --> 02:04:46.977
Let's go.

1977
02:04:50.927 --> 02:04:54.362
Oh God. this is it. The pyramids built
right over the machine.

1978
02:04:54.397 --> 02:04:55.869
They turn that machine on...

1979
02:04:57.566 --> 02:04:58.614
no more sun.

1980
02:05:01.245 --> 02:05:02.639
Not on my watch.

1981
02:05:02.766 --> 02:05:05.808
Not on my watch.

1982
02:05:16.614 --> 02:05:19.543
- USS Stennis. identify.
<i>- Hey. where the hell are you?</i>

1983
02:05:19.733 --> 02:05:20.565
<i>What. you're on a weather channel?</i>

1984
02:05:20.605 --> 02:05:22.667
<i>Sports center.
"I dream of Jeannie" or something?</i>

1985
02:05:22.697 --> 02:05:24.376
We get a pretty hundred satellites up there.

1986
02:05:24.468 --> 02:05:26.860
Where the hell are all our men?

1987
02:05:27.071 --> 02:05:28.640
Identify yourself.

1988
02:05:28.900 --> 02:05:30.236
What is your name. sailor?

1989
02:05:30.682 --> 02:05:35.847
Wilder. Captain of the
USS John C. Stennis Aircraft Carrier.

1990
02:05:36.973 --> 02:05:38.510
Okay. Captain Wilder.

1991
02:05:38.561 --> 02:05:41.030
<i>this is Agent Seymour Simmons.
head of the Sector Seven.</i>

1992
02:05:41.140 --> 02:05:43.514
<i>There is a mother
of all non-biologicals</i>

1993
02:05:43.549 --> 02:05:45.342
<i>getting ready to blow up our Sun.</i>

1994
02:05:45.636 --> 02:05:47.233
You wanna fool around
about my lack of clearance.

1995
02:05:47.268 --> 02:05:49.512
or you want to help save a gazillion lives?

1996
02:05:50.146 --> 02:05:52.531
Alright. Agent Simmons.
I'm listening.

1997
02:05:59.741 --> 02:06:01.079
Five klicks.

1998
02:06:01.377 --> 02:06:02.534
<i>West of the gulf.</i>

1999
02:06:02.535 --> 02:06:05.469
<i>We got ourselves a dalion*
remodelling a pyramid.</i>

2000
02:06:05.953 --> 02:06:08.959
I want hopes of prototype weapon
called a rail gun.

2001
02:06:09.020 --> 02:06:10.832
***

2002
02:06:10.882 --> 02:06:11.802
That's classified.

2003
02:06:11.853 --> 02:06:15.721
Don't talk to me about classified. alright?

2004
02:06:15.756 --> 02:06:17.491
Now if you've got a battleship in the gulf

2005
02:06:17.955 --> 02:06:19.006
equipped with that weapon.

2006
02:06:19.056 --> 02:06:21.293
you tell 'em to ready that weapon!

2007
02:06:22.303 --> 02:06:24.726
Contact Destroyer.
USS Kit.

2008
02:06:27.066 --> 02:06:28.800
This way!
Move it!

2009
02:06:30.773 --> 02:06:32.541
What do you need here?

2010
02:06:33.014 --> 02:06:34.704
Let's go! Go!

2011
02:06:38.527 --> 02:06:40.049
Give me your talk.
Come on.

2012
02:06:40.084 --> 02:06:40.786
Epps!

2013
02:06:45.628 --> 02:06:46.918
Right now.
we need air support.

2014
02:06:48.113 --> 02:06:49.379
That ship's in contact.
20 miles--

2015
02:06:49.848 --> 02:06:52.020
Grid on contact.
Proceed 88. Alpha Sierra.

2016
02:06:56.001 --> 02:06:57.207
USS Stennis 0-9-0.

2017
02:06:57.357 --> 02:07:01.249
you are approved to drop
a 2.000 pound [bomb].

2018
02:07:07.270 --> 02:07:08.553
- What you got?
- A detonator. sir.

2019
02:07:08.554 --> 02:07:10.590
They're 600 meters away and
they're heading right for the pillars.

2020
02:07:10.625 --> 02:07:11.326
Alright.

2021
02:07:12.036 --> 02:07:13.435
Precious cargo's coming.

2022
02:07:13.715 --> 02:07:14.521
Move!

2023
02:07:41.108 --> 02:07:41.994
Sam!

2024
02:07:42.289 --> 02:07:43.455
Spotted Sam.

2025
02:08:15.615 --> 02:08:16.154
Come on!

2026
02:08:16.155 --> 02:08:18.968
2-2. covering fire.
Two civilians. twelve o'clock.

2027
02:08:27.260 --> 02:08:28.255
Cover for us.

2028
02:08:35.286 --> 02:08:38.266
Call the air strike.
We'll rescue the civilians.

2029
02:08:57.813 --> 02:08:59.681
Come on. Get up!

2030
02:09:00.114 --> 02:09:00.816
Come on!

2031
02:09:01.905 --> 02:09:02.606
Get in here.

2032
02:09:03.422 --> 02:09:04.603
Oh look who showed up.

2033
02:09:04.865 --> 02:09:06.960
You better have a good reason
for us to be here.

2034
02:09:06.992 --> 02:09:07.884
Where's Optimus?

2035
02:09:08.114 --> 02:09:09.954
He's right over there.
across the courtyard.

2036
02:09:11.068 --> 02:09:11.949
I got to get to him right now.

2037
02:09:11.984 --> 02:09:13.404
No. we got an air strike coming.

2038
02:09:13.405 --> 02:09:14.883
I have to get to him right now.

2039
02:09:16.969 --> 02:09:18.435
Come here.
b-back.

2040
02:09:28.489 --> 02:09:30.068
Incoming!

2041
02:09:34.058 --> 02:09:37.004
Behold to the only Jetfire!

2042
02:09:38.198 --> 02:09:41.860
Now let me show you
how we brought them pain in my day.

2043
02:10:01.554 --> 02:10:03.224
I'm too old for this crap.

2044
02:10:03.274 --> 02:10:04.295
Keep going.

2045
02:10:04.296 --> 02:10:05.649
15 minutes of fighting.

2046
02:10:25.811 --> 02:10:29.628
I am directly below the enemy's scrotum.

2047
02:10:30.384 --> 02:10:32.591
<i>25.7 metres above sea level.</i>

2048
02:10:32.643 --> 02:10:33.782
<i>29.32 north.</i>

2049
02:10:33.817 --> 02:10:36.003
- Field track. 5-2. 0500 o'clock.
- Target acquired.

2050
02:10:36.075 --> 02:10:37.192
Killing track two.

2051
02:10:37.380 --> 02:10:39.205
<i>Lock. Fire.</i>

2052
02:10:54.211 --> 02:10:56.173
Yeah! Yeah!

2053
02:10:56.208 --> 02:10:59.884
<i>B-1. stand on my target.
30 seconds. 2000 pounds inbound/i>

2054
02:10:59.934 --> 02:11:02.117
We're gonna make a break
for the beast on my command. okay?

2055
02:11:02.167 --> 02:11:04.039
You guys stick with me.
you understand?

2056
02:11:04.074 --> 02:11:05.056
You stay on my ass.

2057
02:11:05.107 --> 02:11:06.887
<i>Watch out for orange smoke.</i>

2058
02:11:06.937 --> 02:11:08.795
Hope these F-16s got good aim.

2059
02:11:08.796 --> 02:11:09.696
Yeah. why is that?

2060
02:11:10.121 --> 02:11:11.752
I told them to hit the orange smoke.

2061
02:11:13.583 --> 02:11:15.178
You mean our orange smoke?

2062
02:11:15.228 --> 02:11:16.998
It wasn't my best toss.
okay?

2063
02:11:17.107 --> 02:11:18.980
<i>Viper. Thunder.</i>

2064
02:11:19.411 --> 02:11:20.232
- Run!
- Run!

2065
02:11:28.713 --> 02:11:30.241
Incoming!

2066
02:11:33.371 --> 02:11:34.072
Come on.

2067
02:12:08.058 --> 02:12:08.987
Die!

2068
02:12:15.966 --> 02:12:17.318
Sam!

2069
02:12:33.396 --> 02:12:35.214
Hold your fire!

2070
02:12:37.455 --> 02:12:38.157
Sam!

2071
02:12:40.159 --> 02:12:42.460
Get out!
Get me an EVAC.

2072
02:12:45.119 --> 02:12:46.644
Can't you do something?

2073
02:13:21.762 --> 02:13:23.825
- Sam! Sam...
- Sam!

2074
02:13:30.503 --> 02:13:33.023
Come on. we got to move.
We got to move! Come on!

2075
02:13:34.575 --> 02:13:35.853
Administer CPR.

2076
02:13:37.042 --> 02:13:38.089
That's our son!
I wanna see my son.

2077
02:13:38.139 --> 02:13:39.095
Sammy!

2078
02:13:42.944 --> 02:13:46.385
Clear! Take a shot.
Clear! Take a shot.

2079
02:13:46.477 --> 02:13:47.635
One. two. three.

2080
02:13:50.757 --> 02:13:51.459
Do it again.

2081
02:13:57.200 --> 02:13:59.043
Sam!

2082
02:14:00.883 --> 02:14:06.032
Okay. listen to my voice.
I love you and I need you.

2083
02:14:06.866 --> 02:14:12.224
Please. please come back to me.
Sam. please! I love you!

2084
02:14:23.994 --> 02:14:25.820
Am I dead?

2085
02:14:26.611 --> 02:14:30.922
We have been watching you.
A long. long time.

2086
02:14:33.212 --> 02:14:35.269
You have fought for Optimus.

2087
02:14:35.441 --> 02:14:39.933
our last descendant.
with courage and with sacrifice.

2088
02:14:39.968 --> 02:14:42.593
The virtues of a leader.

2089
02:14:43.049 --> 02:14:46.163
A leader worthy of our secret.

2090
02:14:46.475 --> 02:14:49.370
The Matrix of Leadership is not found.

2091
02:14:49.892 --> 02:14:51.311
It is earned.

2092
02:14:52.407 --> 02:14:54.686
Return now to Optimus.

2093
02:14:55.321 --> 02:14:57.564
merge the Matrix with his Spark.

2094
02:14:58.256 --> 02:15:02.952
It is. and always has been.
your destiny.

2095
02:15:07.758 --> 02:15:08.745
Sam.

2096
02:15:15.096 --> 02:15:16.433
I love you.

2097
02:15:55.316 --> 02:15:58.225
Boy. you returned for me.

2098
02:15:59.675 --> 02:16:01.688
A living Prime!

2099
02:16:03.217 --> 02:16:05.656
I don't believe it.

2100
02:16:15.841 --> 02:16:18.241
My Matrix.

2101
02:16:23.719 --> 02:16:25.019
Get up. get up.
get up. get up.

2102
02:16:26.239 --> 02:16:27.506
Get up. Prime!

2103
02:16:29.299 --> 02:16:32.802
- Oh. no.
- He's turned on the machine.

2104
02:16:33.607 --> 02:16:35.329
You gotta stop him.
Get up!

2105
02:16:35.650 --> 02:16:37.203
Optimus!

2106
02:16:39.287 --> 02:16:41.763
Fallen. my master.

2107
02:16:41.934 --> 02:16:46.267
My brothers could not stop me from this.

2108
02:16:47.282 --> 02:16:51.835
- Yes.
- Now I claim your sun.

2109
02:16:54.700 --> 02:16:56.369
Enemy target.
top of pyramid.

2110
02:16:56.370 --> 02:16:58.527
Engage.
engage. engage.

2111
02:17:03.890 --> 02:17:06.811
In moments.
we'll be at firing strength.

2112
02:17:22.533 --> 02:17:24.184
In all my Decepticon life.

2113
02:17:24.259 --> 02:17:26.990
I never did a thing worth doing.
until now.

2114
02:17:27.764 --> 02:17:30.545
Optimus. take my parts.

2115
02:17:30.759 --> 02:17:33.660
And you'll have a power
you've never known.

2116
02:17:34.577 --> 02:17:36.755
Fulfill your destiny.

2117
02:17:42.793 --> 02:17:47.051
Jolt. electrify!
Transplant those afterburners.

2118
02:18:05.644 --> 02:18:07.288
Let's roll.

2119
02:18:09.754 --> 02:18:11.608
Fire. Take off to the pyramid!

2120
02:18:23.670 --> 02:18:27.315
This planet will be dark forever.

2121
02:18:49.669 --> 02:18:51.914
Die like your brothers.

2122
02:18:52.523 --> 02:18:54.831
They were your brothers too.

2123
02:19:23.469 --> 02:19:25.753
Starscream!

2124
02:19:38.659 --> 02:19:40.719
You picked the wrong planet!

2125
02:19:43.661 --> 02:19:45.660
Give me your face.

2126
02:19:54.131 --> 02:19:58.264
I rise.
You fall.

2127
02:20:00.358 --> 02:20:03.556
No. No.

2128
02:20:05.040 --> 02:20:09.791
Not to call you a coward.
Master. but sometimes

2129
02:20:09.791 --> 02:20:13.509
cowards do survive.

2130
02:20:14.045 --> 02:20:15.977
This isn't over.

2131
02:20:43.436 --> 02:20:46.267
It took all of this for you
to tell me that you love me.

2132
02:20:47.984 --> 02:20:49.454
You said it first.

2133
02:21:40.898 --> 02:21:43.307
Thank you. Sam.
for saving my life.

2134
02:21:44.766 --> 02:21:45.467
You're welcome.

2135
02:21:46.799 --> 02:21:48.536
Thank you for believing in me.

2136
02:21:53.259 --> 02:21:57.898
<i>Our races united by a
history long forgotten</i>

2137
02:21:57.899 --> 02:22:01.205
<i>and a future we shall face together.</i>

2138
02:22:01.934 --> 02:22:06.195
<i>I am Optimus Prime.
and I send this message</i>

2139
02:22:06.225 --> 02:22:09.466
<i>so that our past
will always be remembered.</i>

2140
02:22:09.467 --> 02:22:12.386
<i>For in those memories.
we live on.</i>

2141
02:22:36.080 --> 02:22:39.580
We're so glad you could join us.
<i>Professor Einstein.</i>

2142
02:22:39.781 --> 02:22:41.781
Yeah. I was kind of busy.

2143
02:22:44.460 --> 02:22:45.960
Okay.
